irusets spredning i Norge og verden|last=Nilsen|first=Av Sondre|last2=Skjetne|first2=Oda Leraan|website=VG Nett|access-date=11 March 2020|last3=Sfrintzeris|first3=Yasmin|last4=R\u00f8set|first4=Hanna Haug|last5=breaking-avdeling|first5=Carina Hunshamar og VGs}}</ref><ref name=VG>{{cite web|url=https://www.vg.no/spesial/2020/corona/ |title=Corona-viruset: Slik spres viruset i Norge og verden. Kart og statistikk |publisher=Vg.no |date= |accessdate=2020-03-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|CZE}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Czech Republic|Czech Republic]]\n|3,257\n|31\n|45\n|<ref name=\"CZE\">{{cite web|url=https://onemocneni-aktualne.mzcr.cz/covid-19|title=P\u0159ehled situace v \u010cR: COVID-19|last=|first=|date=27 March 2020|website=mzcr.cz|language=cs|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=27 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|DNK}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Denmark|Denmark]]\n|2,860\n|90\n|2\n|<ref name=\"STPS numbers\" />\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|ROU}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Romania|Romania]]\n|2,460\n|86\n|252\n|<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.digi24.ro/stiri/actualitate/informatii-oficiale-despre-coronavirus-ministerul-de-interne-26-de-persoane-sunt-in-carantina-2077-sunt-monitorizate-la-domiciliu-1266261 |title= Latest updates on COVID-19 (Coronavirus) | website=Digi24 |access-date=13 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|Ireland}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the Republic of Ireland|Ireland]]\n|2,415\n|36\n|5\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.ie/en/news/6c3762-statement-from-the-health-protection-surveillance-centre-saturday-14/|title=Statement from the National Public Health Emergency Team|website=www.gov.ie|access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|POL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Poland|Poland]]\n|2,347\n|35\n|35\n|<ref name=\"PL205_5\" />\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|LUX}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Luxembourg|Luxembourg]]\n|1,988\n|22\n|40\n|<ref>{{cite web | url=https://msan.gouvernement.lu/en/dossiers/2020/corona-virus.